These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-1::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, scientific, adventure, satire, drama
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, blend, baccarat, bolivar, ritmeester, aristoff
 1. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 2. the person watching adventure movies is not the blend-smoker##6
 3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the bolivar-smoker is not the person watching mystery movies##6
 7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 9. the aristoff-smoker is not the person watching satire movies##6
10. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
12. the person watching scientific movies is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person watching documentary movies##2
13. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
14. the alhambra-smoker is not the person watching adventure movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |      5      |      6      |
| Hobby         | adventure | drama | mystery     | scientific | documentary | satire |
| Nationality   | bolivar    | blend   | ritmeester | aristoff | baccarat    | alhambra   |

