.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis, dahlia, poppy, balloon-flower, zinnia
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: snowboarding, volleyball, swimming, tennis, rugby, parkour
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 9. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
13. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who growspoppy##1
14. the person who growsdahlia is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
15. the person who growsaconite is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is parkour##2
16. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |    3    |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Food    | dahlia | aconite     | balloon-flower   | poppy | amaryllis      | zinnia  |
| Hobby   | parkour   | rugby | snowboarding | swimming  | volleyball | tennis |

