.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, november, september, july, august, december
6 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, hamster, bird, rat, lizard
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is not the owner of the lizard##6
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the rat##1
 6. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the lizard and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality   | august  | july | november    | september | april | december |
| Sport         | rabbit | bird | lizard | rat     | hedgehog  | hamster    |

