.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, soul, techno, hip-hop, disco, metal
There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, italian, nigerian, spanish, australian
 1. the fan metal is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
 2. the spanish is on the left of the fan techno##1
 3. the fan techno is on the right of the fan metal##1
 4. the australian is in an even position##4
 5. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5
 6. the italian is on the right of the fan ambient##1
 7. the fan ambient is not the italian##6
 8. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the australian is not the fan ambient##6
10. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the mexican##3
11. the fan soul is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
12. the chinese is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
13. the fan metal is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5
14. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2    |       3        |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food   | disco | hip-hop | metal         | techno | ambient     | soul      |
| Job    | nigerian   | australian | spanish | mexican    | chinese | italian |

