The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, lawyer, mechanic, analyst, chef, software-developer
 1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 2. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
 3. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 5. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 6. the analyst is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
 7. the bartender is between the chef and the analyst##2
 8. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
 9. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
10. the lawyer is not the mexican##6
11. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3    |    4    |      5      |       6       |
