.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: indie, jazz, ambient, folk, funk, classical
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: scientific, documentary, animation, time-travel, disaster, drama
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the fan funk##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is between the fan classical and the fan jazz##2
 3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is not the fan jazz##6
 5. the fan classical is not the person watching disaster movies##6
 6. the fan classical is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the person watching drama movies is the fan funk##1
 8. the fan classical is on the right of the fan folk##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the fan ambient##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is the fan jazz##1
11. the person watching documentary movies is not the fan ambient##6
12. the fan indie is somewhere to the right of the fan folk##5
13. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |  3   |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | ambient  | funk | folk | classical | indie | jazz |
| Pet        | time-travel | drama  | animation | documentary | disaster  | scientific          |

