The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, handball, biathlon, cricket, parkour
 1. the owner of the cat is between the person who's sport is parkour and the owner of the horse##2
 2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is not the owner of the dog##6
10. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
13. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |      3      |      4      |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | pony | mouse | dog      | rabbit      | cat       | horse   |
| Hobby      | cricket        | biathlon  | climbing | parkour | handball | sailing |

