.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |   4    |    5    |      6      |
| Beverage      | video-games | gardening | chess | card-games | board-games | camping |
| Music-Genre   | soccer  | rugby   | volleyball | baseball  | ice-hockey  | handball        |

