.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-19::.
There 6 different types of food: peas, raspberry, apricot, nectarine, cucumber, banana
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
 1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 4. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 5. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 8. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
10. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
13. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
15. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
16. the person eating nectarine is not the person drinking juice##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | apricot     | raspberry | banana  | nectarine | cucumber   | peas |
| Sport         | 7up | tea  | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | lemonade | juice  |

