.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-20::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, october, march, may, july, june
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, action, scientific, family, spy
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is not the person watching family movies##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 8. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 9. the person watching spy movies is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
10. the person watching action movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
12. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
13. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | july | june | march | december | october | may |
| Music-Genre   | horror | action        | family     | spy | scientific      | thriller |

 